import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Buttom from './Buttom'
import { Headerblock } from './Headerblock'


const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Headerblock/>
        <Buttom/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Home
const Container = styled.div`
height: 100vh;`
